    <!-- ================================================================
         BROWSE SECTIONS — reels & videos the user can browse by theme.
         Six top-level sections (display_context = 'BROWSE'):
           POLITICS | ENVIRONMENT | GOVERNMENT | MEDIA | JUDICIARY | CITIZEN
         Each media item links to a structured owner (media_owners) so the
         "who owns this" attribution shows in the Instagram-style viewer.
         All seeded APPROVED so they appear in the public feed immediately.
         ================================================================ -->

